s cyclical or persistent.\n\n## v9shadow Candidates (Emerging)\n\n- **v9shadow-velmono-dev** (score 94.27, STRENGTHENING): n=82, drop_top3=+2.54, monthly=4.05 SOL. The top-ranked strategy by composite score; ~18 trades to n=100. Watch closely.\n- **v9shadow-velmid-liq-mono** (score 83.32, STABLE): n=83, drop_top3=+1.25, monthly=3.64 SOL (just below 3.75 bar). Still needs ~17 trades and a monthly lift.\n\n## INVALID Strategy Count\n\n**34 enabled strategies have n≥100 with drop_top3≤0.** These include the entire v41-holders family (15–19), v42-breakeven family (10–40), all v39 entry-gate variants, v35/v37/v43 variants, and the live strategy v44. Running them continues to consume DB cycles, inflate shadow P&L visibility, and — critically for v44 — burn real SOL. Full kill list in recommendations below.\n\n## Operator Next Step\n\n1. **Immediate**: Review and approve kill of v44-climb-1s-ttp10-live-micro (live, losing money).\n2. **Batch kill**: Approve the 33 remaining INVALID shadow strategies listed in recommendations.\n3. **Watch**: v9shadow-velmono-dev needs ~18 more trades — no action needed, just monitor.\n4. **Hold on v25 promotion** until the DECAYING flag clears for 3+ consecutive days.\n",
